snippet.title: Castle Story - Trailer
snippet.description:
Our Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SauropodStudio
Our Twitter : http://twitter.com/SauropodStudio
Our Website : http://www.sauropodstudio.com
This is the first trailer of our new game Castle Story. This game is a mix between a real time strategy game and a voxel based game. We hope you like it! Let us know!
